-- Shares of Brazil builder MRV jump on earnings beat
-- 
-- Fri Aug 15, 2014 09:15AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, Aug 15 (Reuters) - Shares of Brazilian homebuilder MRV Engenharia e Participacoes SA <MRVE3.SA> jumped in opening trade on Friday after the company beat profit expectations for the second quarter. [ID:nL2N0QK1HU]

